DASHBOARD QUALITY CHECKLIST
================================================================================

Before generating dashboard code, verify:

1. TYPOGRAPHY ‚úÖ
   [ ] Sidebar brand uses font-display
   [ ] All page headings use font-display
   [ ] All metric numbers use font-display
   [ ] Table headers use text-muted-foreground

