   [ ] Using shadow-card + hover:shadow-hover
   [ ] Icons use text-primary color
   [ ] Trend indicators with proper colors

3. TABLES ‚úÖ
   [ ] Rows have hover:bg-secondary/50
   [ ] Rows have hover:shadow-hover
   [ ] Headers styled with text-muted-foreground
   [ ] Proper border colors (border-border)

4. SIDEBAR ‚úÖ
   [ ] Navigation items use rounded-xl
   [ ] Active state has shadow-card
   [ ] Hover states are smooth
   [ ] User profile card has hover effect

5. SPACING ‚úÖ
   [ ] Stats grid uses gap-8
   [ ] Content sections use gap-8
   [ ] Cards use p-8 internally
   [ ] Sections have py-24 or py-32

6. COLORS ‚úÖ
   [ ] Using semantic colors (text-muted-foreground)
   [ ] Charts use primary gradient
   [ ] No hardcoded color values
   [ ] Consistent color scheme throughout

7. CHARTS & VISUALIZATIONS ‚úÖ
   [ ] Use primary color for main data
   [ ] Include proper legends
   [ ] Add tooltips for details
   [ ] Show loading states

8. INTERACTIONS ‚úÖ
   [ ] All buttons have proper variants
   [ ] Forms use consistent styling
   [ ] Empty states are beautiful
   [ ] Loading states use skeletons

Generate dashboards that feel professional and premium! üìä
